{"type":"weapons","title":"Gold Bow","summaries":["The <b>Gold Bow</b> is a strong type of <linked>bow</linked> crafted using <linked>Gold Bars</linked>, and is one of the strongest types of <linked>ore</linked> bows before one is able to obtain <linked>Demonite</linked> or <linked>Crimtane</linked>. It is the counterpart to the <linked>Platinum Bow</linked>, yet is beaten by it in power and speed. Its sole purpose is to fire <linked>arrows</linked> from a distance at enemies and deal damage to them.","Its best <linked>modifier</linked> is <b>Demonic</b>, as it does not have any knockback and thus cannot get modifiers that affect it. <span class=\"eico i3 i5 i6\" title=\"Old-gen console, 3DS and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> It can also get the <b>Deadly</b> modifier, which, while the Demonic modifier may provide the greatest damage per hit, grants a higher increase to the overall <abbr title=\"Damage per second\">DPS</abbr>."],"statistics":{"Uses ammo":"<linked>Arrows</linked>","Damage":"11 <span class=\"small-bold\">(Ranged)</span>","Knockback":"0 <span class=\"knockback\">(No knockback)</span>","Critical chance":"4%","Use time":"26 <span class=\"usetime\">(Average)</span>","Velocity":"6.6","Rarity":"<span class=\"rarity\"><linked>[img:Rarity level: 0]</linked></span>","Sell":"<span class=\"coin\" title=\"14 Silver Coins\" data-sort-value=\"1400\"><span class=\"sc\">14</span></span>","Research":"<abbr class=\"journey\" title=\"Journey Mode\">1 required</abbr>"},"crafts":{"Recipes":[{"result":{"rowspan":1,"value":"<span class=\"i multi-line\"><linked>[img:Gold Bow]</linked><span><span><linked>Gold Bow</linked></span></span></span>"},"ingredients":{"value":"<ul><li><span class=\"i\"><linked>[img:Gold Bar]</linked><span><span><linked>Gold Bar</linked></span></span></span> <span class=\"note-text\">(7)</span></li></ul>"},"station":{"rowspan":1,"value":"<span class=\"i\"><linked>[img:Iron Anvil]</linked><span><span><linked>Iron Anvil</linked></span